terraform is called as a infrastructure as a cod (IAC) . it is used to improve your infrastructure deployment and imporove your scability it means instead of going to aws for gcp and creatring manually we can do it by writing a code.
we create modules based on company standards devoplopers use them based on there requirment. it manages IAAS  PAAS SAS.

what is state file
it requires state to manage and store information about  resource and infrastructure that using with terraform. we cant use terraform without state. by default state is stored locally on the directory 

what is terrafrom module
A Terraform module is a set of Terraform configuration files in a single directory. Even a simple configuration consisting of a single directory with one or more .tf files is a module. 

